Dirb (Kali pre-install, attempts a brute-force file enumeration on the target host):

dirb <target_ip> -r (non-recursive)

Gobuster (go-based file enumeration with extra features):
- apt install golang
- export GOPATH = /root/go
- mkdir /root/go
- go get && go build
- go run main.go
- go build
- ./gobuster -u <ip> -l -w <wordlist-location> -x <file extension> -t 20

